OL,3,CFire crews in attendance at major
OL,4,CBelfast blaze
OL,6,FA large fire has broken out in the
OL,7,Fdocks area of Belfast.
OL,9,FA total of 60 fire fighters and nine
OL,10,Fpumping appliances are currently
OL,11,Ftackling the blaze at Clearway Metal
OL,12,FRecycling on the East Twin Road.
OL,14,FNo injuries have been reported.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
