OL,3,CFire crews in attendance at major
OL,4,CBelfast blaze
OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for the
OL,7,Ffire service said: "Northern Ireland
OL,8,FFire and Rescue Service are currently
OL,9,Fengaged in firefighting operations to
OL,10,Fextinguish a fire in a large quantity
OL,11,Fof scrap metal at Clearway Metal
OL,12,FRecycling, East Twin Road, Belfast.
OL,14,F"A total of 9 pumping appliances, an
OL,15,Faerial appliance, high volume pump and
OL,16,F60 firefighters are engaged in
OL,17,Ffirefighting operations".
OL,19,F"The fire is in a pile of scrap metal
OL,20,Fmeasuring approximately 50m x 50m".
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@XO]{D@AOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
