OL,3,CFire crews in attendance at major
OL,4,CBelfast blaze
OL,6,F"Crews are utilising a high volume
OL,7,Fpump to convey water to the fire".
OL,9,F"There are no reported injuries and
OL,10,Fall persons are accounted for."
OL,12,F"Operations will continue for some
OL,13,Ftime. Members of the public are
OL,14,Fencouraged to stay away from East Twin
OL,15,FRoad and keep windows and doors
OL,16,Fclosed."
OL,18,FThe PSNI and Harbour Police have also
OL,19,Fadvised motorists to avoid the area
OL,20,Fand seek an alternative route for
OL,21,Fjourneys.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@aO]qD@AOUrD@_O]tD@AOUxD@HO]
