OL,3,CFire crews in attendance at major
OL,4,CBelfast blaze
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Belfast Harbour
OL,7,FPolice said: "We are working closely
OL,8,Fwith PSNI, Northern Ireland Fire and
OL,9,FRescue Service, and staff of Clearway
OL,10,FDisposals following the outbreak of a
OL,11,Ffire at its scrap metal recycling
OL,12,Ffacility in the Harbour Estate.
OL,14,F"Queen's Road has been closed to
OL,15,Ftraffic and pedestrians. We would
OL,16,Fadvise local residents in the
OL,17,Fsurrounding area to keep windows and
OL,18,Fdoors closed as a precautionary
OL,19,Fmeasure and for people to avoid the
OL,20,Farea."
OL,26,@oD@NOU
